{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Riches From the Deep</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A rich reward awaits those daring enough to dig. The deeper you go, the greater the rewards\u2014and the risks. Anything could be down there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/deep2.png?t=1739824726\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build to Survive</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build scaffolding, piping and lighting to increase your odds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/BuildPipes.gif?t=1739824726\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Trade For Supplies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep your reputation up to buy tools for your dig.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Time Passes When You Die</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are no checkpoints in The Last Dig, only new explorers to find your buried corpse years later. Will you find your treasure before Earth is sealed off forever?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Beware Shifting Rock</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earthquakes can trap any explorer in the depths. Stay nimble, don't suffocate, and survive The Last Dig.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3205800?t=1739824726","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739824726","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/87bcffd2debd1f7141f58586baf74b55700eaf39/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739824726","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/87bcffd2debd1f7141f58586baf74b55700eaf39/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739824726","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","de